div.p:
Augustine the Italian Monke (that of some hath bin taken
for the Apostle of Englande) demaunded of Pope Gregorie,
Gregor. lib. 12 Indict. 7. Iewel in defens. Apolog. Pag. 765. Inter decret. Zachariae. by way of great councel, whether a womanne wyth Childe mighte be Baptized or not: and howe long afterwarde it myghte be lawfull for hyr to come to the Church.
